ygData.subject: Re: Qyenos Merchant that sells tiny daggers?
ygData.msgSnippet: there is nowhere in qeynos that sells tiny daggers. take the boat to erudin (2nd stop) and stock up on tiny daggers. you can also get a nifty robe that is ac 6
ygData.messageBody:
there is nowhere in qeynos that sells tiny daggers. take the boat to erudin
(2nd stop) and stock up on tiny daggers. you can also get a nifty robe that
is ac 6 and mana +2.

Qorona of the Volition Guild, 15th lvl (or 16th depending on the time of
day, hehe) enchanter on Cazic-Thule
